---
title: HelloHero: Italian Pork Orecchiette with Baby Leaves & Cheddar Cheese
description: Pasta with a cheesy tomato sauce, veggies and the pork, all packed into one amazing piled-high pasta. If that’s what you were hoping for then this dish won’t disappoint you!

